OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudier day, with
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of rain, this mostly
OL,7,Flight but perhaps a few heavier
OL,8,Foutbreaks developing over Lothian and
OL,9,FBorders. West coast perhaps
OL,10,Fbrightening up later. Rather humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few showers continuing this
OL,13,Fevening. The Central Belt should
OL,14,Fbecome dry overnight, but some low
OL,15,Fcloud. Perhaps the odd thundery shower
OL,16,Fover Dumfries and Southern Borders.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FAny low cloud burning off to
OL,19,Fleave a dry bright day with some sunny
OL,20,Fspells. Very warm to hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
